@startuml SME_Ops_Sequence_Register
title UC1 — Register organization and owner — §2.3.7

actor Guest
participant "Web UI" as Web
participant "AuthController" as API
participant "AuthService" as Svc
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Guest -> Web : submit registration form
Web -> API : POST /auth/register
API -> Svc : register(dto)
Svc -> Auth : createUser(email, password)
Auth --> Svc : auth user id
Svc -> DB : $transaction\nOrganization + User(OWNER)
DB --> Svc : org + profile
Svc --> API : tokens + user
API --> Web : 201 + JWT
Web --> Guest : redirect /dashboard

@enduml
